---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { CONTACT } from "../constants/contact";
---

<Layout
  title="Our Philosophy"
  description="Discover the philosophy of Kiyora Wellness - a harmony of old and new."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="relative h-[60vh] min-h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540555700478-4be289fbecef?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="Kiyora Spa Interior"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"
      />
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-charcoal-900/80 via-charcoal-900/50 to-charcoal-900"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-20">
      <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-white mb-6 tracking-widest leading-tight"
      >
        The Spirit of Kiyora (清ら)
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 font-light font-serif italic">
        Where the ancient art of Japanese healing meets modern luxury.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-900 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-gold-muted mb-8 tracking-wider"
        >
          Our Philosophy
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mb-6 font-serif">
          The Harmony of Old & New
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            "Founded on the principle of 'Sei' (Balance), Kiyora Spa strives to
            offer more than just a massage; we offer a return to self. Just as
            Sundari blends tradition with modernity, we synthesize time-honored
            Japanese techniques like Shiatsu pressure points and Takumi
            stretching with the refined comfort of a world-class luxury
            sanctuary.
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe that true relaxation comes from the alignment of 'Ki'
            (Life Energy). Every ritual, from our synchronized couple massages
            to our silent oil-free therapies, is designed to unblock this
            energy, ensuring you leave not just rested, but deeply restored."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="order-1 md:order-2 relative h-[500px] rounded-sm overflow-hidden bg-charcoal-800"
      >
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600334129128-685c5582fd35?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Massage Therapy"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 border border-gold-muted/30 m-4 rounded-sm pointer-events-none"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Sanctuary Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-800 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div
        class="relative h-[500px] rounded-sm overflow-hidden bg-charcoal-900"
      >
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519823551278-64ac92734fb1?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Hot Stones"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 border border-gold-muted/30 m-4 rounded-sm pointer-events-none"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-gold-muted mb-8 tracking-wider"
        >
          The Sanctuary
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mb-6 font-serif">
          A Retreat for the Senses
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            "Stepping into Kiyora is stepping out of Ahmedabad and into a realm
            of stillness. Our space is designed around the concept of 'Kanso'
            (Simplicity). We have merged sleek, modern minimalism with natural
            elements warm timber, soft washi-paper lighting, and organic stone
            textures to create an ambience that quiets the mind the moment you
            arrive.
          </p>
          <p>
            Unlike the bustling city outside, our private suites are acoustic
            sanctuaries. Whether you are indulging in a Private Jacuzzi Soak or
            a silent meditation, the design of our spa serves a single purpose:
            to protect your peace."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Takumi Standard Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-900 relative">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-gold-muted mb-8 tracking-wider"
        >
          The 'Takumi' Standard
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mb-6 font-serif">
          The Art of Skilled Touch
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-white/70 font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            "In Japanese culture, 'Takumi' refers to an artisan who has mastered
            their craft. At Kiyora, our therapists are not just staff; they are
            practitioners of Takumi.
          </p>
          <p>
            With a quality of service designed to rival five-star international
            hotels, we pride ourselves on intuitive care. We do not believe in
            'standard' treatments. Whether you need the deep pressure of our
            Muscle Recovery Massage or the gentle flow of our Swedish Ritual,
            every stroke is adjusted to your body's unique language."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="order-1 md:order-2 relative h-[500px] rounded-sm overflow-hidden bg-charcoal-900"
      >
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
          alt="Spa Ingredients"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
        />
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 border border-gold-muted/30 m-4 rounded-sm pointer-events-none"
        >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ingredients Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-800 relative">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-gold-muted mb-6 tracking-wider"
        >
          Our Ingredients
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white font-serif">Purity in Every Touch</h3>
        <p class="mt-6 text-white/70 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          "We strictly adhere to the philosophy of 'Midori' (Nature). We believe
          that what goes on your skin should be as pure as nature intended."
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-charcoal-900 p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-gold-muted/30 transition-colors group"
        >
          <h4
            class="text-lg font-serif text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-muted transition-colors"
          >
            Custom Blends
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white/60 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We do not use generic lotions. Our warm herbal oils are curated to
            soothe specific muscle groups, mirroring the 'Onsen' (Hot Spring)
            experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-charcoal-900 p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-gold-muted/30 transition-colors group"
        >
          <h4
            class="text-lg font-serif text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-muted transition-colors"
          >
            Organic Origins
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white/60 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our body polishes use premium natural ingredients inspired by the
            Sakura (Cherry Blossom) for hydration and Green Tea extracts for
            detoxification.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-charcoal-900 p-8 border border-white/5 hover:border-gold-muted/30 transition-colors group"
        >
          <h4
            class="text-lg font-serif text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-gold-muted transition-colors"
          >
            Freshness
          </h4>
          <p class="text-white/60 font-light text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Just as a chef respects their ingredients, our therapists respect
            the oils and scrubs, preparing them fresh to ensure their healing
            properties are at their peak.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-charcoal-900 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-white mb-6 tracking-widest"
      >
        Your Sanctuary Awaits
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 font-light mb-10 text-lg">
        Step away from the chaos and reconnect with your inner peace. Reserve
        your private ritual today.
      </p>
      <a
        href={`https://wa.me/${CONTACT.WHATSAPP_NUMBER}?text=Hello%20Kiyora%20Wellness%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20reserve%20a%20ritual.`}
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-gold-muted text-charcoal-900 hover:bg-white transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest font-medium text-sm"
      >
        Book Your Escape
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
